content: You're so lucky! Some of my friends went and they all said it was an unforgettable experience. I am living in cold Amsterdam, and the population here is only around 800 thousand people. It's mind blowing to realize that a crowd bigger than Amsterdam gathered in Copacabana to watch Madonna ðŸ¤©
